{"title":"朝霞的呼唤——在《中国儿童报》创刊５０周年之际致全国小朋友","authors":["聪聪"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":1,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝霞的呼唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——在《中国儿童报》创刊５０周年之际致全国小朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聪聪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，是时候了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们来讲一讲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《中国儿童报》的故事。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海，１９４６年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧中国一片黑暗——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷孩子成千上万"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜流浪在街头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没衣服穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃不上饭……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但！曙光在前——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党党员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和她的拥护者们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在为黎明而战；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那天——２月１６日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然有一张"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《新少年报》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在上海的一些小学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在旧中国的街头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在孩子们的眼前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮起旗帜一面！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它像一缕朝霞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向孩子们宣告："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是新时代的报刊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是新少年的伙伴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，叔叔阿姨们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒着被杀头的危险"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把这张报纸创办；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，坏蛋们害怕了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚刚出满一百期"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就强迫它停了刊……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到上海解放后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它才又和孩子们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥抱又见面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！建立了新中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它搬家到北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了中华各民族的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更多的小朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到改名为《中国儿童报》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到有成百万的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新朋友的今天……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编者们老了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代又一代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用青春和汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把它培育和浇灌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小读者成材了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代又一代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"源源去接班……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半个世纪啊，五十年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少编者和家长的心血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少老师和辅导员的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的关怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的期盼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全都通过它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作“五爱”和“三好”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作灿烂的明天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又在向“跨世纪公民”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤：中华！腾飞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加油！向前……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}